title: Rhythm of the Zeit 1/10: Sleeping Beauty, Neil Peart, Kendrick Perkins, Selena Gomez, Marianne Williamson

description:
On this edition of the Rhythm of the Zeit Jack and Miles discuss the Sleeping Beauty proposal, Neil Peart has passed away, Kendrick Perkins getting into it with Kevin Durant on Twitter, Selena Gomez album release, and Marianne Williamson has suspender her campaign for presidency.
